<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idf688b83a-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5" identifier="/us/usc/t46/s9306"><num value="9306">§ 9306.</num><heading> State regulation prohibited</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">A State or political subdivision of a State may not regulate or impose any requirement on pilotage on the Great Lakes.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idf688b83b-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5">(<ref href="/us/pl/98/89">Pub. L. 98–89</ref>, <date date="1983-08-26">Aug. 26, 1983</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/97/559">97 Stat. 559</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
